        "created_at": "2020-04-09T17:08:23.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I am torn between which one to buy. Seems like both have had good showings of late. I am leaning towards<br>\nthe PL simply because of my love for PL.<br>\nAny thoughts? Well, besides BUT BOTH (which would make the most sense.)<br>\nThank you in advance!</p>",
