        "id": 2861883,
        "name": "Robert Sand",
        "username": "Robert_Sand",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/r/9e8a1a/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-04-10T08:29:44.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Guigal !<br>\nI did not taste the Hermitage, but the Cote-Rotie 1980 was still very nice last year, and Hermitage should be stronger.<br>\n1980 Bordeaux are disapointing thru and thru - cannot imagine PL being better.</p>",
